# R3 — normalize line endings. Store text as LF in the repo and check it out as
# LF on every platform, so a Windows checkout no longer triggers the
# "LF will be replaced by CRLF" warnings on every `git add`.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets — never touch (git auto-detects most, but be explicit).
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary
*.mp3 binary
*.wav binary
*.ogg binary
